Calls forth a wave of energy that heals a target and bounces to nearby friendlies. Each bounce heals less damage. If the last healed unit dies within 20 seconds, the wave continues on to nearby targets.

Calls forth a wave of healing energy that bounces up to 5 times. The primary target is healed for 100, each subsequent bounce heals 10% less. If the last healed unit dies within 20 seconds, the wave continues on to nearby targets.
